from its source to be treated.

80
00:05:54,450 --> 00:06:03,270
All it takes is for a bomb to hit
the pumping station or water pipe,

81
00:06:03,270 --> 00:06:08,950
and the supply to 100,000 people
is cut off.

82
00:06:08,950 --> 00:06:17,280
Sadly, water supplies often
become strategic targets in conflict.

83
00:06:17,280 --> 00:06:23,290
You cut the water and
you immediately drive people away.

84
00:06:23,290 --> 00:06:26,910
The ICRC has a key role to play.

85
00:06:26,910 --> 00:06:35,240
