in Gaza despite the blockade.

95
00:07:32,490 --> 00:07:38,940
that also enabled us to begin talks
with the Israeli authorities.

96
00:07:38,940 --> 00:07:46,510
We succeeded in bringing in the machinery
needed to complete the treatment plant.

97
00:07:47,720 --> 00:07:49,540
